<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">首数相同，尾数和小于10的两个两位数相乘时，先求出首数的平方加上尾数之积，再加上尾数之和与首数的乘积，此数即为所求之积。可利用公式</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">10a×10a+bc+(b+c)×10a</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">进行速算，其中a表示首数，b、c分别表示被乘数与乘数个位上的数字，且b+c小于10。</Run>
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">62×67=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 62×67</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=60×60+2×7+(2+7)×60</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=3600+14+540</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=4154</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>